title: Healthy Ep. 1 - How We Really Change
description:
How do we change? Let's start this season by talking about the power of the Holy Spirit and our role in the process of change.

Verses: 2 Peter 1:3-9, 1 Samuel 17, 2 Timothy 1:7
John Elmore's sermon: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-law-and-spirit-romans-7-1-7/id76017520?i=1000535205237
